channel.title: Fuck sakes
channel.description:
Well, my racing career is over, come last night..
Some fucking pricks captured my dogs, and threw them out ages away from my house (we are still yet to find them), and got into our driveway and stole our bike trailor. This was locked, so they've broken that.
Overall the contents of that trailor was 40 grand.
We had a 102 cm television, xbox 360, 2 motorbikes, one being mine which is fully modified for racing, factory suspension and everything. Probably 15 grand just there, then there's my little brothers bike.
So basically, my racing career, the only thing I've ever done, and have loved from the minute go, is fucking over.
Whoever stole my trailer, I hope you enjoy them. As you have destroyed all the hope in this 14 year old's heart.
